
Get the WM8960 soundcard source code. and install all linux kernel drivers


git clone https://github.com/waveshare/WM8960-Audio-HAT
cd WM8960-Audio-HAT
sudo ./install.sh 
sudo reboot


after installing these drivers in linux kernel one should manually Check that the sound card name matches the source code wm8960-soundcard.

pi@raspberrypi:~ $ aplay -l

pi@raspberrypi:~ $ arecord -l
